page.title: 10Halezowin - Halesowen
page.content:
*** Halezowins Futbawl Teem ***
On Sataday 27th ov April 1985, Halezowin Tane futbawl teem went to Wemblie tu play in vu F.A.Varze agenst Fleetwud Tane. Farzends ov fans went tu serport ther local teem. Ver woz grate tentchon as vay kicked off at free o'clock.Halezowin stated vu match strongli and wivin ten minits Gef Mos scored Halezowins fust gowl. Ven we completele tuk ova and on fifti and ayti minits Ley Joynsan scored Halezowins secund and fird gowl. Fleetwud scord a lait consalashun gowl and ver was grate jubilashun at vu final whisle. Vis win maid up for vu defeet in 1983 agenst V.S. Rugby wen Rugby's gowl waz off-side.
